This is a photo and a video sharing application to picasa and youtube respectively.

////////TO PICASA/////////////////////

1.To share photo run onclick.py.
2.Enter the credentials and then press ok.
3.Then enter the image path
4.Then press ok.Credentials will be asked only once and then it will use the stored credentials.
5.Photo will be uploaded to picasa account

/////////TO YOUTUBE/////////////////

1.To share video run onclick_youtube.py.
2.Enter the credentials and then press ok.
3.Then enter the video path
4.Then press ok.Credentials will be asked only once and then it will use the stored credentials.
5.video will be uploaded to youtube account


